                    "name": "Activate",
                    "ability_type": "offensive",
                    "action_type": {
                        "type": "stat_block_section",
                        "subtype": "action_type",
                        "name": "One Action"
                    },
                    "frequency": "once per hour",
                    "effect": "The *inspiring spotlight* emits a 5-foot burst of bright magical light within 120 feet. If the burst intersects with an area of magical darkness, the *inspiring spotlight* attempts to counteract the darkness with a +17 modifier. Creatures within the burst gain a +1 item bonus to saving throws and Charisma-based skill checks. The spotlight remains lit for 1 minute or until you Interact to turn it off. During this time any creature adjacent to the spotlight can move the burst up to 20 feet from the burst\u2019s original position with an Interact action.",
